{
  "stem": "20088.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 29.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were really agents with this hiding place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when we had gone to visit, they followed us so that they knew where we were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So then my father-- of course, we-- there was no way-- no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father tried to bribe them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He-- you know, he said, if we pay you, would you let at least the children go, or things like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they said no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But he made a deal with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, if he would give them money or jewelry or something, the Reitsmas would-- could go free.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So my father said, yes, that's-- that's fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had-- in-- we had a powder box, a talcum powder box.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and you could open it to refill it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in that box, we had hidden diamonds and jewelry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was where we lived from, that was hidden there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was at the Reitsmas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So an SS man and my mother went back to the Reitsmas and fetch this powder box.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans took it and opened it and pocket it, the jewelry, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And let the Reitsmas go free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, they needn't have done that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could have-- but at least there, they kept their word.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at least they were saved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know the name anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after the war, there was a court case when we returned, because my mother-- at the time, of course, we didn't know the name.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- I don't know exactly how it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they did find her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was-- my mother went to court.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she had helped-- because she had-- as a double agent, you have to do-- to get into the underground movement, you had to go-- do good things.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
